  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All patients must fulfill the clinical criteria for diagnosis of Crohn's disease.

          -  Subjects must have inactive CD as defined by CDAI &lt; 150

          -  CRP &lt;/=10 mg/L.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant and lactating women.

          -  Known hypersensitivity to vitamin D.

          -  Hypercalcaemia

          -  Current supplemental intake of vitamin D3 &gt;800 IU/D.

          -  Diagnosis of any of the following: active tuberculosis, sarcoidosis,
             hyperparathyroidism, pseudohyperparathyroidism, renal failure or malignancy, active
             TB, sarcoidosis, lymphoma.

          -  Participation in a concurrent clinical trial.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
